ygData.messageBody:
Someone stated earlier that there are only 2 high level dungeons for all
those lvl 50's out there. Well actually there are many more, the cities of
races that are KoS to you and your friends. I have already seen Teir'dal in
North Freeport killing the paladins there. I know of at least 2 attempts by
good players to breach the gates of Neriak. Personally I am looking forward
to storming the foul holes the Trolls and Orges call home.

And if nothing else this should get this thread KABOINGed hehe.
